hellip;仲有無論多複雜既法寶，只要多啦A夢講解一次就能運用自如，甚至會改良用法令多啦a夢一吃一驚&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n神記憶：只要出現過既法寶，大雄都可以講出名稱同埋用法&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n高速回復能力：無論比狗咬，比人打，甚至高處墮下搞到遍地鱗傷，只要數分鐘就可以恢復，印象中大雄亦未出入過醫院&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n快速睡眠：唔駛多講，都市人羡慕既能力&nbsp;"},{"pid":"60d9f6e1f783266f36e92aa3cddaedbbb38a090f","tid":584240,"uid":29304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7345c89abb2026ec1eb939f17fe148025d9e0ad1","tid":584240,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T17:38:15.000Z","msg":"點都唔乞人憎多過出木杉"},{"pid":"652b2097d9f368df22b2117a11e433b408df6545","tid":584240,"uid":139974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03f9fcd839dfc5520686c1ddbd79dacc346a9749","tid":584240,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T17:17:33.000Z","msg":"唔知點解諗起首歌<a href=\"https://youtu.be/meRAC3XcZXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmeRAC3XcZXg&d=YlEOpzoS0lMG%2FjhymmpRW8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b4b47a8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/meRAC3XcZXg</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T01:36:27.000Z","msg":"呢首正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582b8ec4b0928e7cd67cc9d357c7197c01d817d6","tid":584240,"uid":139974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7345c89abb2026ec1eb939f17fe148025d9e0ad1","tid":584240,"uid":30847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T17:38:15.000Z","msg":"點都唔乞人憎多過出木杉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T01:37:28.000Z","msg":"人地都係毒撚一個，咩都屌打大雄條垃圾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}